		(property "Description" "Teensy 4.0 development board (600MHz Cortex-M7, socketed). Symbol vendored from XenGi/teensy_library (MIT), pin numbering per PJRC pinout cards rev2; pins renamed/relaid for this project. Pins 35-54 (bottom-side SMT pads) and 15-19 (the 5-pad short-end row: VBAT, VDD, GND, PROGRAM, ON_OFF) removed to match the Teensy40_Socketed footprint and keep schematic-parity clean. 15-19 dropped 2026-07-22 to free routing area: 16/17 were stacked duplicates of the VDD/GND on pins 31/1/32, and VBAT/PROGRAM/ON_OFF are unused on this design."
